title: DAZ3D - Universal Horns for Genesis 3 Female(s)
description:
Universal Horns for Genesis 3 Female(s) is a great props pack, with 7 conforming Horns sets that have head HD morphs to match. There are 7 different texture sets that are interchangeable between all horns set. Horns will match any Genesis 3 Female shape, and is future proof so they will work with any new shape. Material are for both Iray and 3Delight. It comes with wearable presets so the horns and morphs automatically apply. A must for all your fantasy scene.

What's Included and Features

Universal Horns for Genesis 3 Female(s): (.DUF)
Bull Horns
Deer Horns
Devil Horns
Goat Horns
Long Horns
Ram Horns
Twisted Horns
Genesis 3 Female Morphs for Universal Horns:
Bull Horns
Deer Horns
Devil Horns
Goat Horns
Long Horns
Ram Horns
Twisted Horns
Textures Include:
9 Texture and Bump Maps (up to 3456 x 2304)
Texture Templates available through the Product Library
Daz Studio 3Delight Material Presets (.DUF)
Daz Studio Iray Material Presets (.DUF)
